{"tid":1328724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論] 點樣破解中聯辦嘅招數？","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T08:05:07.000Z","uid":39205,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"02ec888a81d2fb5e980d9da0f30e3d8220420b2e","tid":1328724,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:08:30.000Z","msg":"見到網評員近期開始大力攻陷連登，又吹風向又分化又失敗論，好彩都有唔少巴打睇穿同埋開post提醒大家，想集中討論下點可以見招拆招。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 失敗論</span></span><br />\n呢個我個人認為算易解決，就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無視佢</span></span>，見到啲標題係咩輸架啦個啲，㩒入去，可以睇下佢講乜先，<span style=\"color: orange;\">睇完負評都唔好㩒，更加唔好留言屌佢幫佢推，我地需要嘅係正能量</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 鳩推post</span></span><br />\n近日都有發現好多舊post或者唔關事嘅post比人係咁推，<span style=\"color: red;\">班三毛已經融左入人群，係到鳩推唔關事嘅post上熱門混淆視線</span>，大家睇post時可睇下個post係幾時開，如果兩三日之前嘅，睇下就算啦日日都有新資訊無必要推舊野，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">睇完出返去幫手推行動post！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3. 半夜轉風</span></span><br />\n辛苦哂啦咁多位三毛，夜媽媽唔訓教都要開工，對付呢招都係要靠大家，<span style=\"color: orange;\">麻煩大家起身返工出門口搭車嘅時間，直接search個啲行動日子，例如721咁，每個post入去推一下</span>，做完啦，先去返熱門好似平時咁碌下。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">4. 搞分化</span></span><br />\n日日都見到有啲post係到屌邊個係鬼邊個係鬼，鬼你老母咩講撚左各有各做，希望大家可以相信自己人。<br />\n<br />\n其實被分化係最嚴重亦都最難破解，始終有時真係大家有大家想做嘅野同時又未必認同對方，但係求下大家記住，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家最終目標一樣，而無人知邊一條路先行到去終點，各有各做，幫到就幫。</span></span>"},{"pid":"45c9708a683c9aab548bdf328b4b7f8744360d7c","tid":1328724,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"如果大家發現有咩新招數或者成個風向有問題，最緊要即刻講出黎，一黃左佢地好難做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f736ad51f0f7e2451c969225e951e0d47ec5cb4","tid":1328724,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"咪撚再推嗰啲失敗post"},{"pid":"e104948c7e60ed73766b6c36967cd3c7492cca67","tid":1328724,"uid":32655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:12:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aebcbee315a6868fb4b416a2dce7356d66d379f6","tid":1328724,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682eab3f6d777e110050eb827ccf950f1b6f729f","tid":1328724,"uid":67332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:19:28.000Z","msg":"<code>新聞po睇日期先覆，有人推舊po、出引戰po、傳聞po唔好覆，前面已經有人講咗「唔好覆」就唔好跟住留「唔好覆」否則你等同推po，一毛點摟屌你一覆就中計。俾正負評前睇埋最後一頁，唔好俾第一頁帶風向。721去遊行！</code>"},{"pid":"9b78ac25b897ded9bb757503fd399b6407cf6078","tid":1328724,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"[7.21 遊行] 好撚重要 必需置頂!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327475</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee39ebcdf05c12e1072359097b0cdb1c08680048","tid":1328724,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"屌我個post係咪比中聯辦block左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ccf8214bb271027b08556b367518056e9c6a3b","tid":1328724,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9d